videos.description: Dwayne Bacon gets a steal then loses the ball on the break but is able to corral it and score the and-1 basket.

videos.description: Al Horford gets the ball at the top of the key, keeping Aaron Gordon off-balance in the triple-threat, then hits a dagger 3-pointer in the final minute of the game.

videos.headline: Horford nails dagger 3 for Thunder
